{"tid":870943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE日本成員宮脇咲良等暫停AKB48活動，IG、Twitter都無得用？","createTime":"2018-10-21T13:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:38:57.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b76f88990196c38a7e7fa96e016e737dd47e3cb3","tid":870943,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"韓國Mnet人氣選秀真人騷《Produce 48》所誕生的女團IZ*ONE將於10月29日正式出道，而日本成員宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子和本田仁美今日在日本出席IZ*ONE出道前最後一次AKB48握手會，<span style=\"color: red;\">之後便會暫停AKB48工作，專注IZ*ONE的活動</span>。三位來自AKB48的成員不止要面對娛樂文化和工作環境的轉變，<span style=\"color: red;\">更重要的是宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子和本田仁美三位將不能隨時隨地更新社交平台，向粉絲交待近況。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1996784/org/e813ffc6739b727e62ed8ecfae559a22.jpg/-Yi9xtAjV2C-kzAFNuwbIrfPh6d8TGm25qVvX-alb18?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1996784%2Forg%2Fe813ffc6739b727e62ed8ecfae559a22.jpg%2F-Yi9xtAjV2C-kzAFNuwbIrfPh6d8TGm25qVvX-alb18%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=aefb751d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為「可以面對面的偶像」，AKB48不但會舉行劇場公演、握手會和演唱會，與粉絲近距離接觸，還會頻繁使用社交平台更新近況，讓粉絲可以知道AKB48成員第一手消息，加強AKB48成員的親民形象；雖然Kpop偶像也有使用社交平台，不過部分Kpop組合的成員會共用同一個社交平台帳號，而不會額外開設個人帳號，例如BTS防彈少年團、MAMAMOO、GFRIEND、Red Velvet等等，就連從《Produce 101》Season 2誕生的國民男團Wanna One的成員也是集中使用同一個帳號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1996650/org/af9ca4c211c63b19d1afbbb118ea9a2c.jpg/oMPy1UnOxcfK-2AZ8Vaw7WNaENXV4ndtDTXi8Q014vE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1996650%2Forg%2Faf9ca4c211c63b19d1afbbb118ea9a2c.jpg%2FoMPy1UnOxcfK-2AZ8Vaw7WNaENXV4ndtDTXi8Q014vE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=bb1b410d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有AKB48粉絲聲稱，本田仁美在握手會上表示被限制使用社交平台，不過仍可透過AKB48 Mail分享日常點滴。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！專任！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdf6034e8e